  <p>
   Suppose you wanted to be very specific or clear about what kind 
of wagon you have.  You can use classifiers (which are special 
handshapes that can be used to show the size, shape, and/or movement 
of things) to describe what the wagon is like.
   <br/>
   <br/>
   "Covered Wagon"
   <br/>
   Sample Description: HORSES "two in far front" "two in near front" 
"behind that, a vehicle" "covered with a high rounded top."
   <br/>
   <br/>
